Copy this whole smart_scaling folder into your spark-1.4.1 folder


Make sure you have installed the sbt assembly (https://github.com/sbt/sbt-assembly)

To start a interactive shell:

	../bin/spark-shell --jars $(echo ./lib/*.jar | tr ' ' ',')

To start a program:

(Make sure you have installed the sbt assembly (https://github.com/sbt/sbt-assembly))

	sbt assembly
	../bin/spark-submit --class "MaxUsage" --master local[*] ./target/scala-2.10/spark-experiment-assembly-1.0.jar
